Who is JR Bob Dobbs? 
~~~~~
Bob is a drilling equipment salesman who, in 1953, saw a vision of God on a television set he had built himself. 
#- The theology holds that Bob is the greatest salesman who ever lived, and has cheated death a number of times. Bob was assassinated by Shadowccon in San Francisco in 1984, though the Church states that he has come back 
#- from the dead several times since then.
