What is Slack? 
~~~~~
Slack is the ability to effortlessly achieve your goals. Dobbs embodies the quality. Slack will allow you to have a free, comfortable life without hard work or responsibility, 
#- which IS YOUR ENTITLEMENT BY BIRTH. This is told to us in Bob's PreScriptures.
